Introduction

Nien is a Taiwanese-Vietnamese singer, rapper and dancer under MODHAUS.

On July 7, 2021, Nien was announced as a contestant on Mnet's survival show "Girls Planet 999". She was eliminated during the second round of eliminations, in the eighth episode.

Nien was introduced as the thirteenth member of the girl group tripleS under MODHAUS on March 20, 2023. She first debuted with the sub-unit LOVElution on August 17, 2023, with the mini album "ↀ (MUHAN)". Nien then made her debut with tripleS on May 8, 2024, with the album "ASSEMBLE24".

As a member of tripleS, Nien was placed in the sub-units LOVElution, Aria, and Visionary Vision.
